    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>This week, a Scottish university and a highly respected respite facility committed to a new partnership which aims to advance person-centred care services for people with neurological conditions like Multiple Sclerosis (MS), stroke and motor neurone disease (MND).</p>]]></Value>
